Table of Contents for current page

Form Field ​

Form Field which you can fill automatically through excel template

Insert Field ​

After filling the form of the site, you have to insert the field of the form, this field is automatic fill. After entering the field name or field type, you can insert the field.

Types of Field ​

  • Basic
  • External
  • Advance
  • Google Field
  • Microsoft Field
  • Scraper Data
  • Program Helper
  • Program Helper - Advance
  • Browser Actions
  • Javascript Dialog
  • Others

Basic ​

  • Text
  • Select
  • Multiple Select
  • Checkbox (Multiple Selection)
  • Radio (Single Selection)
  • Date
  • Button
  • Upload File

External ​

  • Material Single Select
  • Material Multiple Select
  • Date Picker
  • Loop

WARNING

Material field type works on Material framework like Vuetify, MUI, React Material, Angular Material, etc.

Advance ​

  • 👩‍💻 Javascript Code
  • 🚀 Function
  • 🔑 Keys
  • 🛑 Form Error Message
  • ✅ Current Entry as Saved
  • 📃 Field Action Status Checker

Google Field ​

  • Single Text
  • Long Text
  • Choice (Radio)
  • Select
  • Multiple Checkboxes
  • Choice Linear Scale (Radio)
  • Multiple Choice Grid (Radio)
  • Multiple Checkboxes Grid (Checkbox)
  • Date/Time
  • Time/Duration
  • File Upload

Microsoft Field ​

  • Single Text
  • Long Text
  • Choice (Radio)
  • Multiple Checkboxes
  • Dropdown
  • Date Picker
  • Rating
  • Sort List
  • Matrix Radio Group
  • Net Promoter Score (Linear Scale Radio)

Scraper Data ​

  • Fetch Text
  • Fetch HTML
  • Scraping Data
  • Scraping Page URL
  • Fetch Table Data in Scraper Data (Portrait)
  • Fetch Table Data in the Response Excel (Landscape)
  • Fetch Header-Value Data

Program Helper ​

  • X-Focus Application Window
  • X-Click (Space Key)
  • X-Paste Text
  • X-WinAlwaysOnTop (Activate)
  • X-WinAlwaysOnTop (Deactivate)

Program Helper - Advance ​

  • X-Send
  • X-MouseClick
  • X-ControlClick
  • X-ImageSearch

Browser Actions ​

  • Capture Tab
  • Go Back to Previous Page
  • Go Forward to Next Page
  • Reload Tab
  • Close Browser Tab
  • Set Download Item File Name
  • Insert CSS

Javascript Dialog ​

  • Alert Dialog
  • Confirm Dialog
  • Prompt Dialog

Others ​

  • Insert/Remove HTML
  • URL Matching
  • URL Open
  • Send Request
  • Web Request Completed
  • Timer Action
  • String Matching
  • String Manipulation
  • Copy
  • Save as PDF
  • Page Loading
  • Toast Notification
  • Target Element For Print
